snippet.textDisplay: From what I can see, Joaquin has reached an impasse. On one hand, going from personality to personality as thoroughly as he does can't be good for your head and he needs time to be himself and recalibrate. On the other hand, it's probably not a good idea to leave this guy alone with his thoughts for any period of time. I hope nothing happens to him.
